<?xml version="1.0" encoding="iso-8859-1"?>
<page title="Gmane">
  <headsection>
    <p>
      Thanks to <a href="http://gmane.org/">Gmane</a>, our mailing lists are accessible with news interface as well.
      Gmane not only provides a two way mail to news interface, but let you read (browse and search) the mail
      archives with Web interface.
    </p>
  </headsection>

  <sections>
    <section title="Browse/search the mailing list archives">
      <p>Choose mailing list:</p>
      <ul>
        <li><a href="http://news.gmane.org/gmane.comp.web.freemarker.user">freemarker-user@lists.sourceforge.net</a></li>
        <li><a href="http://news.gmane.org/gmane.comp.web.freemarker.devel">freemarker-devel@lists.sourceforge.net</a></li>
      </ul>
    </section>

    <section title="News interfaces">
      <p>All interfaces are two-way (you can both write and read).</p>
      <ul>
        <li>For freemarker-user@lists.sourceforge.net:<br/>
            <a href="nntp://news.gmane.org/gmane.comp.web.freemarker.user">nntp://news.gmane.org/gmane.comp.web.freemarker.user</a></li>
        <li>For freemarker-devel@lists.sourceforge.net:<br/>
            <a href="nntp://news.gmane.org/gmane.comp.web.freemarker.devel">nntp://news.gmane.org/gmane.comp.web.freemarker.devel</a></li>
      </ul>
    </section>
  </sections>

</page>